const opps = $('Get Top Opps').all().map(i => i.json);
const risks = $('Get Risk Context').all().map(i => i.json);
const pressure = $('Get Deadline Pressure').all().map(i => i.json).filter(p => p.opp_title);

const oppSummary = opps.map((o, idx) => {
  const deadline = o.days_to_deadline != null ? `${o.days_to_deadline} days` : 'No deadline';
  const capture = o.has_capture_plan ? `Pwin: ${o.recommended_pwin || '?'}%` : 'NO CAPTURE PLAN';
  return `${idx+1}. [ID:${o.id}] ${o.opp_title} | ${o.agency} | ${o.gda_label} ${o.gda_score}/100 | $${(o.estimated_value||0).toLocaleString()} | Deadline: ${deadline} | ${capture} | Stage: ${o.stage}`;
}).join('\n');

const riskSummary = risks.filter(r => r.title).map((r, idx) => {
  return `${idx+1}. [${r.severity}] ${r.title} | Mitigation: ${r.mitigation}`;
}).join('\n');

const pressureSummary = pressure.length > 0 ? pressure.map((p, idx) => {
  const parts = [`${idx+1}. [${p.pressure}] ${p.opp_title} | ${p.agency}`];
  if (p.days_out != null) parts.push(`DEADLINE IN ${p.days_out} DAYS (${p.response_deadline})`);
  if (p.gate_overdue) parts.push(`GATE REVIEW OVERDUE (was ${p.gate_review_date}, stage: ${p.gate_stage})`);
  parts.push(`${(p.estimated_value||0).toLocaleString()}`);
  return parts.join(' | ');
}).join('\n') : 'None';

const prompt = `You are GDA Command's daily action intelligence engine for Shawn, President of Envision Innovative Solutions (EIS). Today is ${new Date().toISOString().split('T')[0]}.

⚠️ DEADLINE PRESSURE — HANDLE FIRST:
${pressureSummary}

TOP PURSUIT/EVALUATE OPPORTUNITIES:
${oppSummary}

OPEN RISKS:
${riskSummary || 'No open risks'}

GENERATE 5-7 SPECIFIC, ACTIONABLE items Shawn should do TODAY. Each action must be:
- Tied to a specific opportunity or risk (include opp ID)
- Have a clear deadline (today, this week, or specific date)
- Include urgency level (URGENT/HIGH/MEDIUM)
- Be specific enough to execute immediately ("Call X person about Y" not "Follow up")

Prioritize:
1. CRITICAL risks and deadline-imminent opportunities
2. PURSUE opps missing capture plans
3. High-value teaming or competitive actions
4. Pipeline development for EVALUATE opps

Respond ONLY in this JSON format, no markdown:
{"actions": [{"action": "specific action text", "urgency": "URGENT/HIGH/MEDIUM", "opp_id": number_or_null, "opp_title": "short title", "deadline": "today/this week/specific date", "category": "Capture/Risk/Teaming/Pipeline/Competitive", "source_link": null}], "summary": "1-sentence executive summary of today's priorities"}`;

return [{json: {prompt: prompt}}];

const response = $input.first().json;
let result = {actions: [], summary: 'No actions generated'};
try {
  const text = response.content[0].text;
  const cleaned = text.replace(/```json|```/g, '').trim();
  result = JSON.parse(cleaned);
} catch(e) {
  result = {actions: [{action: 'Failed to parse AI response', urgency: 'HIGH', opp_id: null, opp_title: null, deadline: 'today', category: 'System', source_link: null}], summary: 'AI action generation failed - check Anthropic API'};
}

// Add source links for opps
const opps = $('Get Top Opps').all().map(i => i.json);
result.actions = result.actions.map(a => {
  if (a.opp_id) {
    const opp = opps.find(o => o.id === a.opp_id);
    if (opp && opp.source_url) a.source_link = opp.source_url;
  }
  return a;
});

result.generated_at = new Date().toISOString();
result.action_count = result.actions.length;

// Build DB rows separately (not returned to frontend)
const today = new Date().toISOString().split('T')[0];
const nextWeek = new Date(Date.now() + 7*86400000).toISOString().split('T')[0];
const rows = result.actions.map(a => ({
  _db_item: (a.action || '').substring(0, 1000),
  _db_deadline: a.deadline === 'today' ? today : a.deadline === 'this week' ? nextWeek : (a.deadline || today)
}));

// Return clean response (no _rows/_summary internals)
return [{json: {actions: result.actions, summary: result.summary, generated_at: result.generated_at, action_count: result.action_count, _rows: rows}}];

